Our Heritage

Twenty companies coming together to reinvent aerospace & defense sounds unlikely, but for us, it’s our story. 
Jack, Leroy, Si and Burt were the names of some of the visionaries who helped set the foundation to create today's Northrop Grumman. Because of their work, the world met groundbreaking innovations such as the Flying Wing and the legendary B-2 Spirit Stealth Bomber.
Learn more about our heritage >>












