Our Values

The women and men of Northrop Grumman Corporation are guided by Our Values. They describe our company as we  want it to be. We want our decisions and actions to demonstrate these Values. We believe that putting Our Values into practice creates long-term benefits for shareholders, customers, employees, suppliers, and the communities we serve.
Learn more about our Values >>













Our Responsibility
At Northrop Grumman, we are committed to maintaining the highest of ethical standards, embracing diversity and inclusion, protecting the environment, and striving to be an ideal corporate citizen in the community and in the world.
Learn more about our Responsibility >>
Northrop Grumman's Corporate Responsibility Reports












Awards and Recognition
We are honored to be recognized for our dedication to excellence and a diverse and inclusive workforce. From the prestigious Robert J. Collier Trophy to our efforts as a Top 100 Military Friendly employer and one of America's premier organizations for diversity, equality and the disabled, you can see why Northrop Grumman is continually recognized as one of the best places to work in the world.
